headline: TA Connections Collaborates with Uber for Business to Help Elevate the Travel Experience for Disrupted Passengers
summary: MIAMI, December 17, 2024--TA Connections integrated Uber rides into TA Disruption Hub, changing the ground transportation experience for passengers during a flight disruption.

headline: Canada’s Finance Minister Chrystia Freeland Resigns From Cabinet
summary: OTTAWA—Canada’s Finance Minister  Chrystia Freeland  quit the Liberal government cabinet Monday, a surprise departure that casts further doubts about how long Prime Minister  Justin Trudeau  can hold on to his job given the government’s deep unpopularity.  The announcement roiled the capital, with one of Trudeau’s most loyal and trusted lieutenants choosing to leave after publishing a stinging letter critical of the government’s direction on fiscal policy.  The move came on the same day Freeland was scheduled to introduce a fall economic statement, which showed sharply wider budget deficits than the government promised just a year ago.
